
# The City of the Sun

A story of a man who finds a lost city in the desert.

=> the_city_of_the_sun.gmi
=> ../../index.gmi

> I have found it. The City of the Sun.

> It is a city of gold and jewels. A city of wonders.

> But it is also a city of ghosts. A city of the dead.

> The people of the city are long gone. But their spirits remain.

> And they are not happy to have a visitor.

> ...a city of secrets... a city of lies...
